{
    "title": "Tea portafilter/Japanese green",
    "author": "Decent",
    "beverage_type": "tea_portafilter",
    "notes": "This profile requires a specially designed tea portafilter that opens its valve at pressures of 3 bar or above.  Put a tea bag or loose leaf tea into the basket.  Makes about 230ml of tea in 3 minutes.  The 2 bar of pressure extract a stronger brew, with different flavors.  You can up the pressure during the infusion steps, if you tighten the screw on your tea portafilter.",
